### Goal

Expose information in GraphQL API whether and what kind of code intel is available for a given list of repositories, a repository, a directory, or a file.

### GraphQL API

```graphql

type CodeIntelSupport {
    searchBasedSupported: boolean
    preciseSupported: "unknown" | "supported" | "3rdparty" // supported: we own indexers, 3rd party indexers
}

extend GitBlob {
  codeIntelInfo {
    support: codeIntelSupport
    lsifUploads: LSIFUploadConnection
  }
}

extend GitTree {
  codeIntelInfo {
    lsifUploads: LSIFUploadConnection
    support: []{
        language: string
        numFiles: int
        coveredPaths: []string
        support: codeIntelSupport
      }
   }
  }
}
```

